{"tid":1474711,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"關於面試一直有個疑問 你有咩問題想問","createTime":"2019-08-15T09:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T18:16:52.000Z","uid":248664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"825b3ead5c59cb21771b6b654ea5d7656bb0be98","tid":1474711,"uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:23:54.000Z","msg":"每次面試都會問 有冇咩問題想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我次次都無問 會唔會無咁好印象分或者比人感覺無準備充足？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一入去面試講明分3part <br />\n第1 自我介紹<br />\n第2 佢鳩問<br />\n第3 你有冇咩問題想問<br />\n<br />\n咁我無問第三part 會唔會比人扣左一part分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34d64ae418c239e748b078ca14a3606f8c0797b","tid":1474711,"uid":224779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:29:48.000Z","msg":"無關係 佢睇完你cv基本上已經決定請唔請<br />\n面試只係睇下你係咪正正常常"},{"pid":"1af01d2ac1b01b0e9eae55460153f92048adf279","tid":1474711,"uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b34d64ae418c239e748b078ca14a3606f8c0797b","tid":1474711,"uid":224779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:29:48.000Z","msg":"無關係 佢睇完你cv基本上已經決定請唔請<br />\n面試只係睇下你係咪正正常常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"漏左講面試係政府工<br />\n先過左筆試再去面試 <br />\n因為佢講明分左3pt，怕佢每pt都計分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f50f9f9bf9700fc7a1a018eddb228e44783f5a","tid":1474711,"uid":124811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:32:24.000Z","msg":"問得好有機會加少少分<br />\n問啲廢野實扣分<br />\n個人認為如果唔係有必要問/有信心令佢覺得你條問題好有用嘅話就不如唔好問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e742050992f785d008ce973a8800f056bb29b5","tid":1474711,"uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8f50f9f9bf9700fc7a1a018eddb228e44783f5a","tid":1474711,"uid":124811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-